<div class="flex justify-center">
  <!-- 左側邊攔 -->
  <div class="fixed left-8">
    <div class="w-[204px] mt-4 mx-2 rounded shadow-md bg-white self-start">
      <span class="m-2 text-lg font-bold">Trending Tags</span>
      <div class="flex justify-between mx-4 my-2 text-sm">
          <button class="uppercase"><%= @tag.name %></button>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-between mx-4 my-2 text-sm">
          <button class="uppercase"><%= @tag.name %></button>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-between mx-4 my-2 text-sm">
          <button class="uppercase"><%= @tag.name %></button>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-between mx-4 my-2 text-sm">
          <button class="uppercase"><%= @tag.name %></button>
      </div>
      <div class="mx-auto divider w-36"></div> 
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 mx-4 text-sm">
        <%= link_to 'Explore' %>
        <%= link_to 'About' %>
        <%= link_to 'Posts' %>
        <%= link_to 'All'%>
      </div>
      <span class="mx-auto ml-4 text-xs text-gray-500">@2023 TechTonic</span>
    </div>
  </div>


  <!-- 標籤和追蹤鈕 -->
  <div class="ml-[208px]">
    <div class="w-[770px] bg-white mt-4 rounded shadow-md text-center pb-2">
      <h1 class="inline mx-auto text-2xl">
        <%= image_tag 'image/Ruby icon', alt: "ruby icon", class: " select-none col-span-2 max-h-20 w-full object-contain lg:col-span-1" %>
        <div class="uppercase"><%= @tag.name %></div>
        <div class="m-2 text-xs text-gray-500">
          <%= @tag.users.size %> followers
        </div>
      </h1>
      <% unless current_user.tags.include?(@tag) %>
        <div class="flex justify-center m-4 mb-4">
          <%= link_to "Follow", tag_follow_path(id: @tag.id), class: "rounded p-2 bg-blue-600 text-white font-medium", data: { turbo_method: "put" } %>
        </div>
      <% else %>
        <div class="flex justify-center m-4 mb-4">
          <%= link_to "Unfollow", tag_follow_path(id: @tag.id), class: "rounded p-2 bg-gray-600 text-white font-medium", data: { turbo_method: "put" } %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <!-- 文章列表 -->
    <div>
      <%= link_to "Last", tag_path(id: @tag.id, order: "desc"), class:"btn btn-xs rounded bg-[#6380F2] border-none mt-2" %>
      <%= link_to "Top", tag_path(id: @tag.id, order: "asc"), class:"btn btn-xs rounded bg-[#6380F2] border-none mt-2" %>
    </div>

    <div>
      <%= render partial: "shared/post_card", collection: @posts, as: :post %>
      <%= paginate @posts %>
    </div>
  </div>


  <!-- 右側邊攔 -->
  <div class="w-[280px] mt-4 mx-2 rounded shadow-md bg-white self-start p-4 text-justify">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">About This Tag</h2>
    Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Consectetur aliquam doloribus reprehenderit reiciendis, dolorem placeat et totam ad corrupti perspiciatis laboriosam excepturi, cum mollitia error nam ratione ipsa veritatis eligendi.
  </div>
</div>